{"tid":1361580,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我條女嫌我唔夠S","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T16:23:47.000Z","uid":157842,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e6ff3eb3d5953b8e1a38ec5b105fdf5353291fad","tid":1361580,"uid":157842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:42:11.000Z","msg":"我同女朋友一齊咗大半年<br />\n大家都讀緊書<br />\n我同佢第一次都係對方<br />\n一路都keep住有扑野<br />\n可能一星期4次左右<br />\n(第一次之後果個月因為新鮮 扑左50次以上)<br />\n呢個月發現佢m底<br />\n事緣之前買咗震蛋同佢玩之後<br />\n就開始有唔同跡象覺得佢M底<br />\n仲有佢竟然唔洗我唸送咩生日禮物<br />\n直接同我講要咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但原來佢想要狗帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢開始提出想比我綁 打 言語abuse<br />\n仲不斷上網搵s/m嘅野<br />\n想我學 跟住嚟做<br />\n但無奈小弟只係個普通男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日鳩痕只係想屌個閪<br />\n對S嘅性趣唔大<br />\n有無巴絲有建議可以俾下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如有無啲咩簡單嘅調教項目可以俾我入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7349fa1e1d83771780820df794dce17cd3eaa95","tid":1361580,"uid":19560,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:43:44.000Z","msg":"送佢上發夢前線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;"},{"pid":"c58dc56db271e94bcafd9baa62752241afed23cd","tid":1361580,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:43:54.000Z","msg":"試下做M比佢S"},{"pid":"58d30eece31d65fba4fb216df7aa6ab41f3d6f6d","tid":1361580,"uid":157842,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c58dc56db271e94bcafd9baa62752241afed23cd","tid":1361580,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:43:54.000Z","msg":"試下做M比佢S"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:47:24.000Z","msg":"都試過一次 但佢都唔係好識"},{"pid":"d53f6cf013384e36c0989317426072eb03879c3b","tid":1361580,"uid":214784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:50:03.000Z","msg":"玩過dt dp未"},{"pid":"3b5878dda1be6596a9eaee7e4312cc8290ebdcb9","tid":1361580,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:55:41.000Z","msg":"屌！我係S但就硬係遇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72c19f45ba6d5d6fb4f022b2eea07cac29c724f","tid":1361580,"uid":157842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d53f6cf013384e36c0989317426072eb03879c3b","tid":1361580,"uid":214784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:50:03.000Z","msg":"玩過dt dp未"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:07:00.000Z","msg":"試過塞手指 同震蛋<br />\n佢又唔係鍾意又唔係唔鍾意 <br />\n淨係話好奇怪<br />\n諗住遲啲買肛塞試試"},{"pid":"410d2526b832143c70007551b3d50fc0aaad9012","tid":1361580,"uid":214784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b72c19f45ba6d5d6fb4f022b2eea07cac29c724f","tid":1361580,"uid":157842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d53f6cf013384e36c0989317426072eb03879c3b","tid":1361580,"uid":214784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:50:03.000Z","msg":"玩過dt dp未"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:07:00.000Z","msg":"試過塞手指 同震蛋<br />\n佢又唔係鍾意又唔係唔鍾意 <br />\n淨係話好奇怪<br />\n諗住遲啲買肛塞試試"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:23:47.000Z","msg":"有d有貓尾嘅肛塞，幾有羞恥感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}